sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook
    participant DSPAPI as DSP API Server
    participant ArgoWF as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Driver as Driver Sidecar
    participant Launcher as Launcher Sidecar
    participant S3 as S3 Storage
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata
    participant PersAgent as Persistence Agent
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant KServe as KServe
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry

    Note over User,ModelReg: Workflow 3: ML Pipeline Execution

    User->>Notebook: Compile pipeline<br/>via KFP SDK v2
    Notebook->>DSPAPI: Submit pipeline YAML<br/>(REST API)
    DSPAPI->>DSPAPI: Store pipeline definition<br/>(MariaDB/MySQL)
    DSPAPI->>ArgoWF: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR

    ArgoWF->>ArgoWF: Parse DAG, determine<br/>step execution order
    loop For each pipeline step
        ArgoWF->>Driver: Create step pod<br/>with driver sidecar
        Driver->>Driver: Resolve input artifacts,<br/>check cache
        Driver->>Launcher: Patch pod spec<br/>with resolved params
        Launcher->>Launcher: Execute user code<br/>(containerized step)
        Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>(HTTPS/443)
        Launcher->>MLMD: Record artifact metadata<br/>+ execution lineage
    end

    PersAgent->>ArgoWF: Watch Argo Workflows
    PersAgent->>DSPAPI: Sync run status to API DB

    User->>Dashboard: View pipeline runs
    Dashboard->>DSPAPI: Query run status + artifacts
    Dashboard-->>User: Show pipeline DAG,<br/>artifacts, lineage graph

    Note over User,ModelReg: Optional: Auto-deploy trained model

    DSPAPI->>ModelReg: Register model artifact<br/>(gRPC/9090)
    DSPAPI->>KServe: Create InferenceService CR
    KServe->>S3: Download model
    Note over KServe: Model deployed for serving
